OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FJurors have retired for a second day
OL,8,Fto consider their verdicts in the
OL,9,Ftrial of a husband and son accused of
OL,10,Fmanslaughter.
OL,12,FThe two men deny charges of
OL,13,Fmanslaughter by gross negligence
OL,14,Ffollowing the death of a 71-year-old.
OL,16,FRobert Christopher Morgan, 61, and 53-
OL,17,Fyear-old David Holyoak are on trial at
OL,18,FCarlisle Crown Court.
