OL,3,CJury retires for second day in trial
OL,4,Cof husband and son accused of
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FThey each deny a charge of
OL,8,Fmanslaughter which alleges that they
OL,9,Funlawfully killed 71-year-old Dorothy
OL,10,FMorgan ` their respective wife and
OL,11,Fmother ` by gross negligence.
OL,13,FA jury has heard that Mrs Morgan was
OL,14,Fadmitted to the West Cumberland
OL,15,FHospital on 25 January, 2021.
OL,17,FShe was found to be in an emaciated,
OL,18,Fmalnourished and severely dehydrated
OL,19,Fstate, weighed only four-and-a-half
OL,20,Fstones and died on 4 February that
OL,21,Fyear.
