OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FIt is alleged by the prosecution that
OL,8,Fhusband Morgan and son by another man
OL,9,FHolyoak ` who lived with Mrs Morgan at
OL,10,Fher Calder Avenue home in Whitehaven `
OL,11,F"completely failed to properly take
OL,12,Fcare of her", or at the very least get
OL,13,Fher some help and that they "left her
OL,14,Fto die."
OL,16,FGiving evidence during their trial,
OL,17,FMorgan and Holyoak both said they were
OL,18,Fabiding by wishes they say were
OL,19,Fexpressed by Mrs Morgan that no
OL,20,Fmedical help be sought and provided.
