OL,3,CJury retires for second day in trial
OL,4,Cof husband and son accused of
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FOver the course of the past three
OL,8,Fweeks, a jury has heard detailed
OL,9,Fevidence in the case. A pathologist
OL,10,Fconcluded the cause of Mrs Morgan's
OL,11,Fdeath was emaciation and neglected
OL,12,Finfected pressure ulcers.
OL,14,FEarlier this week, prosecution and
OL,15,Fdefence lawyers in the case delivered
OL,16,Fclosing arguments before Her Honour
OL,17,FJudge Goddard KC gave legal directions
OL,18,Fand summed up the evidence.
